data.description:
Great Value and End of Cul-De-Sac Location.  Nicely kept 3 bedroom and 2.5 bathroom, end unit townhome.  Features vinyl floors, new water heater, new furnace, new cement patio, and new gutters. All bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with laundry area upstairs.  Large master bedroom with wall of closets and generous sized bathroom.  One car garage with extra parking space.  
Makes a wonderful home or investment property.
